Author: setniessesed
Text: Sometimes when I get really intense cravings I'll look up aesthetic pics of food and just stare. Which in turn makes the cravings 1000x worse. Been keeping myself from doing that because I know what the result is. I did watch a recipe vid for some kind of Korean milk bread the other day tho...I need to get over my unrequited love for bread ðŸ˜­

Text: I do the opposite and trigger myself not to eat. But yes, on purpose.
